ganglia-metrics (1.0-2) edgy; urgency=medium

  * Add dependency on gmond so install doesn't fail
  * gmetricd doesn't remove the pid file in all cases, so add --oknodo
    to start-stop-daemon to gracefully fail stopping the daemon if it's
    not running
  * The executable path is not /usr/sbin/gmetricd but python, so
    use --name instead of --exec in the restart init script action

 -- Mark Bergsma <mark@wikimedia.org>  Sun, 14 Jan 2007 14:42:59 +0000

